2A">S shifts left.</text><text x="620" y="123" font-size="13" font-weight="600" fill="#0F172A">Excess demand at old P₁.</text><text x="620" y="152" font-size="12" font-weight="800" fill="#94A3B8" letter-spacing="1.5">NEW EQUILIBRIUM</text><text x="620" y="183" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#059669">Price:     RISES ↑</text><text x="620" y="203" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#DC2626">Quantity: FALLS ↓</text><text x="620" y="223" font-size="13" font-weight="600" fill="#0F172A">P₂ > P₁  ·  Q₂ < Q₁</text></g></g></svg>"`;

